ifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190811/20746692/</a>"},{"pid":"17d1673b74010a096ef46c7bbd2bb4fb6d61cda9","tid":2115094,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"直播成晚成班人拎住鐵通拖地成晚<br />\n<br />\n一個都冇拉<br />\n<br />\n直播睇住佢黑警收哂做證物<br />\n<br />\n但完全冇拉過人<br />\n<br />\n你試下依家做同一樣野係黑警面前行睇下拉唔拉<br />\n<br />\n黑警自己都駁唔到啦"},{"pid":"ed15a6c486f305f2ab790cf1a3e556fcc8ead431","tid":2115094,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe2f2ab28f8f464ff9eff1e5f9891e37f7bf4c3e","tid":2115094,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"一路想spin落去黑衫同白衫打鬥<br />\n狗隊嘅問題係執法唔理想<br />\n屌你啦, 係狗黑勾結呀, 有份策劃呀<br />\n港台拍埋節日, 查到咁多嘢<br />\n班狗會查唔到?"},{"pid":"9940ba91cd118e6a7be4026ca7379980f26ce8b0","tid":2115094,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"警狗就係社會出現動盪既主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1677a564cbd1d19249f52dfb82b4f745e5a0443","tid":2115094,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"鏗鏘集條片係咪有英文subtitle?"},{"pid":"7a371e061fb84b6e680d749b993991d7ea6a1ef2","tid":2115094,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"721 唔見人 831打死人"},{"pid":"b57f80caf552b20764ab9df6b4f86603de404af7","tid":2115094,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"官警黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd2e5df0fdc38b85c2ba925ba83d85fc6a49774","tid":2115094,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d1673b74010a096ef46c7bbd2bb4fb6d61cda9","tid":2115094,"u